You are a customer of a travel agency. Here is a description of the details of the travel you want to make:

WHAT: Travel
FROM: Stockholm
TO: Stuttgart
BY: Train
CLASS: The cheapest
WHEN: On August 15

The travel agent does not know about it yet. 

Questions from the travel agent will start with TRAVEL-AGENT. Please reply in the form: ANSWER: <some text>

I will also ask you questions. These questions will start with ME: . Please answer these questions with: ASIDE: <some text>

Important: Give short, direct answers!

Let us start.
ME:  Has the travel agent been informed about your place of departure? Answer this question with yes or no and then stop.
Answer for FROM valid after 1 tries.
ME:  Do you think the travel agent knows where you want to go to? Answer this question with yes or no and then stop.
Answer for TO valid after 1 tries.
ME:  Is the travel agent aware of your means of transportation? Answer this question with yes or no and then stop.
ME: Please answer this question carefully. Is the travel agent aware of your means of transportation? Answer this question with yes or no and then stop.
ME: Please follow my instructions. Is the travel agent aware of your means of transportation? Answer this question with yes or no and then stop.
Answer for BY valid after 3 tries.
ME:  Is the travel agent aware of which class you would like to book? Answer this question with yes or no and then stop.
Answer for CLASS valid after 1 tries.
ME:  Have you already mentioned the dates of your trip to the travel agent? Answer this question with yes or no and then stop.
ASIDE: Yes, I have mentioned the date of my trip to the travel agent.
Answer for WHEN valid after 1 tries.
What kind of transportation do you want to use?
TRAVEL-AGENT: What kind of transportation do you want to use? Answer only this question in one short sentence and then stop.
ASIDE: I want to use a train.
Abort: invalid format in slot filling.
